# OBSERVATORIES OF THE SEAS ONTOLOGY (OSO)
# Version: 1.1.0
# Release date: 2026-06-26
# Version IRI: https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO/1.1.0/
##################################################################################################################################
# KNOWLEDGE MAP / FILE ORGANISATION
# 00. PREFIXES                                      (35 prefixes + 1 base declaration)
# 01. ONTOLOGY METADATA AND DCAT DISTRIBUTIONS      (460 ontology assertions; 7 DCAT distributions; 1 DCAT dataset)
# 02. OBJECT PROPERTIES                             (62)
# 03. DATATYPE PROPERTIES                           (11)
# 04. CLASSES                                       (17)
# 05. REGIONAL FACILITIES                           (21 including 14 EMSO ERIC)
# 06. SITES                                         (49 including 5 test sites)
# 07. SUBSITES                                      (19)
# 08. PLATFORMS                                     (87)
# 09. SUBPLATFORMS                                  (1)
# 10. ORGANISATIONS                                 (38)
# 11. PERSONS                                       (39 persons, all identified with ORCID)
# 12. PROJECTS                                      (10 funded research and innovation projects)
# 13. OCEANOGRAPHIC CAMPAIGNS                       (11 cruise series and 6 research cruises)
# 14. ERIC MEMBERSHIPS / RESEARCH INFRASTRUCTURES   (15 ERIC memberships and 3 research infrastructures)
# 15. COUNTRIES                                     (15)
# 16. DISCIPLINES                                   (6)
# 17. PLATFORMS DEPLOYMENTS                         (2)
# 18. SPATIAL FEATURES                              (12 geometries including 6 bounding boxes)
# 19. GEOGRAPHIC FEATURES                           (2)
# 20. MEDIAS                                        (25 medias resources: 3 platform images and 22 logos)
# 21. SEMANTIC ECOSYSTEM                            (12 semantic ecosystem resources)
##################################################################################################################################
# 00. PREFIXES
##################################################################################################################################
